data.description: Welcome to 4595 Conrad Road! This single story home boasts 3 large bedrooms and 2 full baths with an open floor plan, providing ample room for relaxation and entertainment. The interior has been completely remodeled: Windows and kitchen were completed in 2016, in 2018 a mini split heating and cooling system was installed, new lighting and furnace in 2022, in 2023 A/C, remodeled bathrooms, paint, stainless steel appliances, interior and exterior doors. Stepping outside you will see the wonderful back yard oasis filled with wildlife, great for the hunting enthusiasts. The massive two tiered deck is exceptional for outdoor gatherings and enjoying the serene surroundings. The above ground pool will help to escape those hot summer days. All of this sits on a 2.5 acres with an oversized 3 car attached garage and an additional two sheds, making it the perfect family home. Did I mention...  the new roof was installed in 2020, siding was done in 2021, in 2022 an additional 50 amp outlet was installed at the corner of garage with two separate clean outs, great for RV parking, and in 2024 a new hot water heater and are having a new well installed. Come see for yourself!
